## Conditional Routing (The Key Pattern)

Graphs **must** use conditional edges to be "smart". Every graph should have at least one conditional routing point.

### Pattern: Read/Write Separation (Fast Paths)

Optimize by detecting read-only queries and skipping expensive processing:

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Read/write separation with fast paths
const routeCondition = (state: typeof ChatGraphState.State): string => {
  const target = state.routingDecision?.target || "respond";
  const operationType = state.routingDecision?.operationType;
  
  log.info("[Graph:RouteCondition] Routing decision", {
    target,
    operationType,
    fastPath: target.includes('_query')  // Flag fast paths
  });
  
  return target;
};

workflow
  .addConditionalEdges("router", routeCondition, {
    intent_query: "intent_query",      // Fast path (DB read only)
    intent_write: "intent_write",      // Full pipeline (inference + verification)
    profile_query: "profile_query",    // Fast path
    profile_write: "profile_write",    // Full pipeline
    respond: "respond_direct",
  });
```

### Pattern: Skip Expensive Operations

Use operation mode to conditionally skip nodes:

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Conditional skipping based on operation mode
const shouldRunInference = (state: typeof IntentGraphState.State): string => {
  if (state.operationMode === 'delete') {
    log.info('[Graph:Conditional] Delete mode - skipping inference, routing to reconciliation');
    return 'reconciler';  // Skip inference entirely
  }
  
  log.info('[Graph:Conditional] Running inference', {
    operationMode: state.operationMode
  });
  return 'inference';
};

workflow.addConditionalEdges("prep", shouldRunInference, {
  inference: "inference",
  reconciler: "reconciler"
});
```

### Pattern: State-Based Branching

Branch based on existing state to avoid redundant work:

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Check state before deciding next step
const checkStateCondition = (state: typeof ProfileGraphState.State) => {
  // If forceUpdate is set with new input, re-generate profile
  if (state.forceUpdate && state.input) {
    return "generate_profile";
  }

  // Profile exists and has embedding
  if (state.profile?.embedding?.length > 0) {
    return "generate_hyde";  // Skip to next phase
  }

  // Need to scrape new data
  return "scrape";
};
```

